<h2 id="sec-1"><span class="section-number-2">1</span> Basic usage</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1">
<ol class="org-ol">
<li>Set up <a href="https://github.com/yoshinari-nomura/org-octopress">org-octopress</a>
</li>
<li>Write your post with 'org-octopress-new-post' command
</li>
<li>Command with 'C-c C-e P x' and type 'octopress' for project to export a HTML file
</li>
<li>Go to octopress root directory and, 'rake preview' or 'rake gen<sub>deploy'</sub>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
